'''阿德伯里'''（'''Adderbury'''）是英國[[牛津郡|牛津郡]]北部的一個[[民政教區|民政教區]]和村莊，由西阿德伯里和東阿德伯里兩部分組成，這兩地還有各自的政府。中間由[[徹韋爾河|徹韋爾河]]的支流“Sor Brook”分隔開來。2010年人口普查時當地有2,819位居民。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11119828&c=Adderbury&d=16&e=62&g=6458264&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1439216348480&enc=1 |title=Area: Adderbury (Parish): Key Figures for 2011 Census: Key Statistics |work=Neighbourhood Statistics |publisher=Office for National Statistics |accessdate=10 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030136/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11119828&c=Adderbury&d=16&e=62&g=6458264&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1439216348480&enc=1 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

